[SHORT DESC]
Prevents switching and increases wild encounter rate.
[LONG DESC]
<p>Enemy Pokémon cannot switch out unless they have the Levitate ability or are part Flying. Pokémon can escape by using Baton Pass.</p>

<p>When a Pokémon with this ability is first in the party, wild encounters have a higher chance of occurring.</p>
<h2>Related Abilities</h2>
<p> <a href="/rs/abilities/shadow_tag">Shadow Tag</a> is almost identical, but  prevents any foe from escaping.</p>